name: The Daily Good 25.2.22
description:
Today the good is this project.

A daily practice of seeing beauty, creating and reflecting on what is good.  

Noticing that life is made up of the tiny moments, book-ended by the bigger ones.

The commitment of showing up for this intentionally everyday.

Seeing a tapestry of moments that have made up a month and recognizing the beauty in each one.  Seeing the repetitive threads showing up.

No matter what the outcome, this IS the good.
